44
00:04:30,288 --> 00:04:31,558
Like you did back in the day?

45
00:04:34,428 --> 00:04:36,899
No.

46
00:04:37,498 --> 00:04:39,199
No, Su Yeon.

47
00:04:55,048 --> 00:04:56,819
You were adopted by this family...

48
00:04:57,618 --> 00:04:59,219
