130
00:14:26,858 --> 00:14:27,888
What?

131
00:14:32,829 --> 00:14:33,858
I was only joking.

132
00:14:37,069 --> 00:14:38,668
Can you text her...

133
00:14:38,669 --> 00:14:40,469
